{"tid":2184601,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"黑暗料理/狗糧 - 農心芝士蛋撈麵 （抄卡幫呢意粉）","createTime":"2020-09-01T15:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T23:06:29.000Z","uid":18844,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"14f84a3e55a33eb4ddc6df8ad406ce0e7b3f8265","tid":2184601,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzWS8s4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzWS8s4.png&h=4179f2c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XyCSo1w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXyCSo1w.png&h=1882d2c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"081f056c0bce13d78607b62dc19a89f3dfa51de5","tid":2184601,"uid":149973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:26:47.000Z","msg":"好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f039204c00923da0978c306d1e987ce99e003a5","tid":2184601,"uid":18844,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"081f056c0bce13d78607b62dc19a89f3dfa51de5","tid":2184601,"uid":149973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:26:47.000Z","msg":"好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T17:21:58.000Z","msg":"好易整😀<br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n1. 辛辣麵*2<br />\n2. 蛋*2<br />\n3. 車打芝士*1～2片 （用芝士碎會方便啲）<br />\n4. 味粉 1包<br />\n5. （可加可不加：鹽、黑椒、辣椒粉）<br />\n<br />\n步驟：<br />\n1. 蛋+芝士+味粉mix好備用<br />\n2. 煮熟啲麵+乾菜，留少少煮完麵的水，約半碗（代替意粉水）<br />\n3. 其餘過多個水倒左去，麵留在熱煲中<br />\n4. 在煲、麵同煮麵水仲有大量餘溫的情況下，加少少煮麵水入啲麵到，一邊mix麵條，一邊把蛋+芝士+味粉混合物 漸漸加入麵條中，直至creamy 🤪<br />\n<br />\n喜歡芝士腸、丸類的朋友可以加多啲料"},{"pid":"9187875dda3628fe62651b7bd74b8f9b039e97e5","tid":2184601,"uid":17426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T17:30:03.000Z","msg":"好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5b016574af1669bc29ff8e06583c6241a84b1b","tid":2184601,"uid":64522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:51:51.000Z","msg":"高汁"},{"pid":"837b41c95f6c885d2175b3a10ffb701894ca2eb3","tid":2184601,"uid":344371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d134209e02f5c8d41e6cc974d75aed45069b8a54","tid":2184601,"uid":47658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015a20cbf159666a82883c002b4ee9758aded666","tid":2184601,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T23:06:29.000Z","msg":"😋😋😋😋😋😋🤤🤤🤤🤤🤤🤤🤤"}]}